<h2>Aside 1.5.8</h2>

<p class="intro">Updates that actually reach you.</p>

<h3>Changed</h3>
<ul>
  <li><b>Update prompts come to the front.</b> When a new version is ready, Aside's update window now opens in front instead of hiding behind your other windows.</li>
  <li><b>A quiet heads-up when an update is waiting.</b> Instead of popping a window on its own, Aside shows a gentle banner in the library and a line in Settings, so you install on your own time.</li>
  <li><b>Readable release notes in dark mode.</b> These notes no longer show up as dark text on a dark background.</li>
</ul>
